mong the Jews are some who, like Saul of Tarsus, are mighty in the </div><div class="t m1bae x26 h24 y1eae ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scriptures, and these will proclaim with wonderful power the immutability </div><div class="t m14d9 x26 h24 y15db ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the law of God. The God of Israel will bring this to pass in our day. His </div><div class="t m2f5 x26 h24 y1434 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arm is not shortened that it cannot save. As His servants labor in faith for </div><div class="t m1892 x26 h24 y1fa6 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those who have long been neglected and despised, His salvation will be re-</div><div class="t m1a0f x26 h24 y1d6f ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vealed.&quot;â€”The </div><div class="t m1a34 x1 h3b y1d6f ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m1ad9 x45 h24 y976 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 380, 381. </div><div class="t m163d x26 h51 y18da ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m226a xad h24 y1c75 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t m19f8 x8a h3b y835 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Acts of the Apos-</div><div class="t mbcb x26 h3b ya86 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tles, </div><div class="t m1350 x60 h24 y11dc ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Salvation to the Jews,&quot; pp. 372-382. </div><div class="t maf3 x26 h24 ya88 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: Although Israel&apos;s rejection of the Messiah resulted in the </div><div class="t me49 x26 h24 y15e2 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">loss of their status as a chosen nation before God, the Lord seeks to lead </div><div class="t m22a6 x26 h24 y1dc0 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Jewish people to salvation through Jesus Christ. Those who believe are </div><div class="t m8ed x26 h24 y1dc1 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">united with believing Gentiles into one body as spiritual Israel. </div><div class="t m162d x71 h51 y12e3 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">76 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000